usage: pytest [-h] -b BROKERS -c ES_CLUSTERS -t TOPICS [TOPICS ...]
              [-g GROUP_ID] [--prometheus-port PROMETHEUS_PORT]

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            show this help message and exit
  -b BROKERS, --brokers BROKERS
                        Kafka brokers to bootstrap from as a comma separated
                        list of <host>:<port>
  -c ES_CLUSTERS, --es-clusters ES_CLUSTERS
                        Elasticsearch servers to bootstrap from as a comma
                        separated list of <host>:<port>
  -t TOPICS [TOPICS ...], --topic TOPICS [TOPICS ...]
                        Kafka topic(s) to read indexing requests from.
                        Multiple topics may be provided.
  -g GROUP_ID, --group-id GROUP_ID
                        Kafka consumer group to join
  --prometheus-port PROMETHEUS_PORT
                        Port to export prometheus metrics over.
